FBIS4-65308 "drweu094_i_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 FRANCE Juppe Rules Out Participation in Haitian Operation Juppe Rules Out Participation in Haitian Operation BR1305120094 Paris LIBERATION in French 13 May 94 p 12 BR1305120094 Paris LIBERATION French BFN [Text] France is "certainly not" prepared to participate in a military intervention in Haiti, [Foreign Minister] Alain Juppe declared in Washington yesterday. He also reiterated Paris' "irreversible" condemnation of the "military regime which has usurped power." The United States has threatened a military operation in Haiti.
